        "description": "Crazy Cook® is a fun and crazy cooking game for the whole family !\nYour goal is to create great recipes…with a twist : the ingredients are a bit hostile !\n\nAre you ready to slice flying pigs with a huge knife ? (workshop 1)\nPeel or block smiling oignons with a peeler ? (workshop 2) \nSmash crazy tomatoes with a hammer ? (workshop 3)\nShoot jumping chickens with a salt mill ?(workshop 4)\n\n10 recipes with 4 workshops each are included : that's 40 ways to have crazy fun ! \n\nCrazy Cook is in early acces. It's only the beginning ! \nWe will soon add 2 new workshops (Pistol shooting and baking). We'll also add new features, new songs, new recipes and new tools ! Stay tuned. \n\nThank you for purchasing the game in early acces. It means the world !",
